{"tid":94641,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳冠希要做爸爸 秦舒培過幾個月生男B？","createTime":"2017-01-25T11:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T16:34:55.000Z","uid":61974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7966c59c4231bc7188ea8eb9f2384b0881ff3013","tid":94641,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"陳冠希喺舊年5月，被《蘋果》踢爆撻着中國名模秦舒培，兩個拍拖年幾，之後又傳出陳冠希同女友喺8月中，斥資285萬美元(約港幣2,250萬)，喺洛杉磯置業築愛巢，好有機會好事近。<br />\n<br />\n而近有人見過秦舒培，仲話佢肚凸凸，有咗幾個月咁，仲傳就嚟生得，一直以嚟都有指想結婚嘅陳冠希，要雙喜臨門，做爸爸同做老襯？《蘋果》聯絡過陳冠希，不過佢就未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170124/56214362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170124%2F56214362&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7HkZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c3fe4ff9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170124%2F56214362&h=442b03ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170124/56214362</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.nosdn.127.net/b1AVAk1e8SO7k0xInhW=Az5TF4KHHlpo8Q5ZQPQkOqNhU1464626998798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.nosdn.127.net%2Fb1AVAk1e8SO7k0xInhW%3DAz5TF4KHHlpo8Q5ZQPQkOqNhU1464626998798.jpg&h=eb02d764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.nosdn.127.net/WW0oXKFcLKVwDlTgNB=utNUEhN=l2qg0otXqNSfGK5Zuw1464626998973compressflag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.nosdn.127.net%2FWW0oXKFcLKVwDlTgNB%3DutNUEhN%3Dl2qg0otXqNSfGK5Zuw1464626998973compressflag.jpg&h=56d0b429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.nosdn.127.net/dG4=ZxLANrK=FUCENsoO92ot9XYSCbz0zgNbpwHPkwE5Q1464626999075compressflag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.nosdn.127.net%2FdG4%3DZxLANrK%3DFUCENsoO92ot9XYSCbz0zgNbpwHPkwE5Q1464626999075compressflag.jpg&h=0113696f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60e868858a68c5ad0d1c9d0